SUMMARY:HBA Series: Overwhelmed to Optimized with AI Powered Content
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T080000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T090000
UID:5227076facedaff1e41c14369f3604fc@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:The Heritage Business Alliance presents: From Overwhelmed to O
 ptimized: Streamlining Your Marketing with AI Powered Content In a digital
  landscape that often feels like a race to keep up\, marketing shouldn't b
 e a chore- It should be a manageable path to growth. Join us for "From Ove
 rwhelmed to Optimized: Streamlining Your Marketing with AI-Powered Content
 \," a strategic session designed to help small-to-medium businesses reclai
 m their time without sacrificing authenticity. We will move beyond the hyp
 e of AI to explore how tools like custom "Gems" and intentional prompting 
 can simplify your content creation\, sharpen your local SEO\, and ensure y
 our brand voice remains consistent across every platform.
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/hba-series-
 overwhelmed-to-optimized-with-ai-powered-content
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Heritage Business Alliance Open Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260323T080000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260323T090000
UID:8bbbc0299760127043c8261812986853@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Heritage area Chamber member businesses are invited to join us
  for this month's Heritage Business Alliance meeting. This open gathering 
 is an opportunity to connect with fellow Heritage businesses and get invol
 ved in shaping initiatives that support the continued growth of the Herita
 ge business community. This month\, we are pleased to welcome Mayor Ben Cl
 apsaddle\, who will join us to hear directly from Heritage-area businesses
  about their experiences\, needs\, and opportunities as an important part 
 of Wake Forest's business landscape. We will also discuss Heritage-specifi
 c goals and projects for the coming months and ways members can help stren
 gthen connections and collaboration within the area. If you do business in
  the Heritage area and want to be part of the conversation\, we invite you
  to join us!
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/heritage-bu
 siness-alliance-open-meeting
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
